00:27:03,006 --> 00:27:04,424
<i>Podes começar.</i>

314
00:27:04,508 --> 00:27:05,717
Olá, pessoal.

315
00:27:08,470 --> 00:27:09,513
CONCURSO STRATFORD STAR

316
00:27:09,596 --> 00:27:12,724
